txt.en: This mark is awarded to those fighting in the Cannuilan campaign, mainly for completing encounters. This campaign consists of Breaching the Necromancer's Gate, Assault on the Ringwraiths' Lair, and Battle in the Tower.\n\nThese can be redeemed for cosmetic rewards at various Skirmish vendors, or redeemed for Skirmish Marks at the Skirmish Exchange vendor.
